{"tid":2014132,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到恐襲點算好","createTime":"2020-05-12T21:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:21:34.000Z","uid":227929,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b969b44b86009c6c022eddf5259d7e004f4f8482","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:06:47.000Z","msg":"1.當面對暴徒以刀<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">棍</span></span>攻擊時 :<br />\n<br />\n攻擊路線通常為上下劈砍或斜下方劈砍，以右手持刀為例，運行路線為右上至左下，防範重點是躲至左前方向下位置、向後退、近身/俯身抱腿 (趁暴徒重心不穩推倒)<br />\n<br />\ni.可用衣物在軀幹前左右快速揮動，以幹擾暴徒攻擊，此外亦可盡量往凶器上纏繞，爭取將刀棍扯離暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cfe05Mc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfe05Mc.jpg&h=a1883901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nii.伺機反擊時，可用拳擊暴徒喉嚨、鼻，或者用手拮其眼部，用硬質物品（如水樽）擊打效果更好。<br />\n<br />\niii.當刀棍將要落下，又無處躲避時，可以兩手曲臂護頭，迎面主動快速貼近暴 (越貼近襲擊者，越避開刀棍鋒芒) 設法與其纏抱在一起，用肩部頂住暴徒腋下，使其不能發力，也可向下踎低 (越低越好) 抱住暴徒雙腿用力回拉，出其不意將其摔倒。 無法貼近暴徒時，可略向後退一步，等刀棍襲擊落空，尚未發起第二次襲擊時，迅速屈臂護頭，迎面貼近襲擊者，與其糾纏在一起，糾纏得越緊越有可能化解危機 。<br />\n<br />\n2.當遭遇化學性恐怖襲擊時<br />\n<br />\ni.呼吸道防護。 如果沒有專業防毒面具，可以利用浸水、檸檬汁、或包有泥土的口罩、紗布、手巾等自製簡易器材，遮掩口鼻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmkLxux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmkLxux.jpg&h=33ce2674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.當面對暴徒揸車衝入人群時<br />\n<br />\ni.如果在廣場，可迅速向較粗壯樹木、水泥路障建築物後躲避，如果在集市，但切記不可緊貼，以防車輛撞擊後產生的衝擊力引致受傷。 亦避免往路燈後、玻璃櫥窗後躲避，以防撞倒撞碎造成二次傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SWrgXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SWrgXQ.jpg&h=69ee031d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcUAaj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcUAaj6.jpg&h=38657a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nii.切記得不要背對車輛逃跑，面向或側向來襲車輛，連續地向左或向右快速移動。 當汽車衝撞你時，連續做&ldquo;之&rdquo;字形或&ldquo;O&rdquo;形移動，可迫使暴徒駕車不停轉向，增加襲擊難度，亦有利於擺脫糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unTX76R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunTX76R.jpg&h=f26036ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWg3jdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWg3jdF.jpg&h=ba57f7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.防止被暴徒沖散<br />\n<br />\n市民可以用右手扯住基他市民嘅皮帶/腰帶，可以防止到暴徒嘅衝擊<br />\n<br />\n最後請大家記得要喺暴徒嘅攻擊下保持冷靜，唔好過度驚慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50de6a357d672e034cd854aea7c0dec4614403f3","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"樓主英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba2b4b1c675505dd93a1e7b1772d4b77457727f","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50de6a357d672e034cd854aea7c0dec4614403f3","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"樓主英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:08:18.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b919fb8cad590174547931b81b86f8e1efc390c","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba2b4b1c675505dd93a1e7b1772d4b77457727f","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50de6a357d672e034cd854aea7c0dec4614403f3","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"樓主英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:08:18.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:08:38.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"adf2521852b4095b7472be28a78afdaa8f5eccb0","tid":2014132,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T21:09:50.000Z","msg":"sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/n